Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.se.inf.ethz.jcd.batman.model.Entry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<Entry>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Directory, File

    public class Entry
extends Object
implements Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<Entry>
    Model (as defined in MVC-Pattern) for a virtual disk entry. This model can be serialized for transportation in case of a client/server architecture.
